  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed rear conservatory, by virtue of its cumulative size, scale, bulk, mass and proximity, would be detrimental to the residential amenities of the adjoining occupiers at 33 Norfolk Road, by reason of overdominance, overshadowing, visual intrusion, loss of light and loss of outlook. Therefore, the proposal would be contrary to Policies DMHB 11 and DMHD 1 of the Hillingdon Local Plan: Part Two - Development Management Policies (2020).",
    "The proposed rear conservatory, by virtue of its cumulative size, scale, bulk, mass and siting, would harm the appearance of the subject dwelling, the visual amenity of the street scene and the character of the North Uxbridge Area of Special Local Character. Therefore, the proposal would be contrary to Policies DMHB 5, DMHB 11 and DMHD 1 of the Hillingdon Local Plan: Part Two - Development Management Policies (2020)."
